   "source": [
    "# What Happens in a Day"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "nyc_data = pd.read_csv(\"/data/bikeshare/data/unified/nyc.csv\")\n",
    "boston_data = pd.read_csv(\"/data/bikeshare/data/unified/boston.csv\")\n",
    "main_data = pd.read_csv(\"/data/bikeshare/data/unified/merged.csv\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 18,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "nyc = {'name':'New York City', 'data':nyc_data, 'ref':'nyc'}\n",
    "boston = {'name':'Boston', 'data':boston_data, 'ref':'bos'}\n",
    "main = {'name':'All Data', 'data':main_data, 'ref':'all'}"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Riders by Hour of Day"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def riders_by_hour(data):\n",
    "    n = 10000\n",
    "    sample = data['data'].sample(n)\n",
    "    times = pd.DatetimeIndex(pd.to_datetime(sample.start_time))\n",
    "    d = sample.groupby([times.hour]).duration.count()\n",
    "    plt.bar(d.index, d/n)\n",
    "    axes = plt.gca()\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Hour of Day\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Percentage\")\n",
    "    axes.set_xlim([0,23])\n",
    "    plt.title(\"Count of Bikeshare Riders in {}\".format(data['name']))\n",
    "    plt.savefig('../images/2/riders_by_hour_'+data['ref']+'.png')\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},

     "data": {

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Riders by Day of Month"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def riders_by_day(data):\n",
    "    n = data['data'].shape[0]\n",
    "    sample = data['data'].sample(n)\n",
    "    times = pd.DatetimeIndex(pd.to_datetime(sample.start_time))\n",
    "    d = sample.groupby([times.day]).duration.count()\n",
    "    plt.bar(d.index, d)\n",
    "    axes = plt.gca()\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Day of Month\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Percentage\")\n",
    "    axes.set_xlim([0,23])\n",
    "    plt.title(\"Age of Bikeshare Riders in {}\".format(data['name']))\n",
    "    plt.savefig('../images/2/riders_by_month_'+data['ref']+'.png')\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    "
   ]

   "cell_type": "markdown",

   "source": [
    "## Riders by Day of Week"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def riders_by_weekday(data):\n",
    "    n = data['data'].shape[0]\n",
    "#     n = 10000\n",
    "    sample = data['data'].sample(n)\n",
    "    times = pd.DatetimeIndex(pd.to_datetime(sample.start_time))\n",
    "    d = sample.groupby([times.dayofweek]).duration.count()\n",
    "    plt.bar(d.index, d)\n",
    "    axes = plt.gca()\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Day of Week\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Percentage\")\n",
    "    axes.set_xlim([0,6])\n",
    "    plt.title(\"Age of Bikeshare Riders in {}\".format(data['name']))\n",
    "    plt.savefig('../images/2/riders_by_weekday_'+data['ref']+'.png')\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]
